(4473, 149668, 'A TASTE OF LIFE', 'A TASTE OF LIFE- an album consisted of all the questions, pain, memories, struggles, flashbacks and bewilderment of an artist/singer-songwriter''s life.  AMA, a devoted artist, spent over 3 years writing and developing this album with a group of renown musicians, Skip Moy on guitar, Jezrael Lucero on keyboards and piano, Anthony Fernandes on drums, Paul Candelaria on bass.  This project has also involved recording in one of Asia''s top notch studios, Hit Productions in Manila, the Philippines, and invited world class musician Ray Obiedo in playing and arranging some tracks on this album.\r\nA mixture of funk, blues, pop & jazz; A TASTE OF LIFE brings you the endless journey of an artist, a singer & a woman finding herself through tasting the reality and the brutal honesty of life.\r\n\r\nRemarks:  This is an album dedicated to AMA''s soon-to-be born son.  Its a gift for him to remind him of the period of time when his mother created this album.  This album is to be released before he''s born :)\r\n', '2012-05-12 00:00:00', 0, 1, 2, '', '', 0, '', 0, 0, '2012-06-02 12:21:31', '2015-02-16 15:48:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(4474, 20248, 'When Teenage', '對於17歲，你有怎樣的記憶？\r\n\r\n那年我們17歲，認識了音樂，也認識了彼此，\r\n組成了爆米花樂團，\r\nWhen Teenage是我們的第一首創作，\r\n寫的是我們17歲時的故事，\r\n就這麼搖搖晃晃地走過了六年時光。\r\n不算短不算長的日子裡，\r\n曾經一起經歷種種不得不劃下休止符的時刻，\r\n我們或許曾改變、懷疑，但從來不曾妥協。\r\n\r\n5/31\r\n爆米花發行成團以來的第一張實體作品，\r\n收錄「When Teenage」、「四季」、「IF」三首歌，\r\n用When Teenage為這張EP命名，紀念當初單純的夢想。\r\n\r\n由清新輕快的旋律配上流行搖滾聲響的氛圍，\r\n結合創造出屬於爆米花簡單直接的風格。', '2012-05-31 00:00:00', 0, 2, 7, '', '', 0, '', 1, 0, '2012-06-03 22:53:25', '2015-02-16 15:48:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
